Overview
The modern portfolio template is designed to showcase my skills, projects, and experiences in a visually appealing and interactive manner. It includes sections for a personal bio, portfolio projects, skills, and contact information.

Features
Responsive design for various screen sizes (desktop, tablet, mobile).
Smooth scrolling and navigation.
Interactive project gallery with modal popups.
Customizable SCSS styles for easy theming.
JavaScript functionality for dynamic content loading.
Setup
To set up the project locally, follow these steps:

Clone the repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/modern-portfolio.git
Navigate to the project directory:

bash
Copy code
cd modern-portfolio
Open the index.html file in your web browser to view the portfolio.

Usage
Customize the portfolio with your own content by modifying the HTML, SCSS, and JavaScript files. Add your projects, skills, and contact information to personalize the portfolio.

